@startuml
title Sequence Diagram (Ripristino Sessione e Query Contestuale) - Iterazione 3

actor Utente                       as U
participant "Browser\n(React App)" as FE
participant "localStorage"         as LS
participant "API Gateway\n(FastAPI)" as GW
participant "JWT Manager"          as JWT
participant "Profile Repository"   as PR
participant "MongoDB"              as DB
participant "Orchestrator Agent"   as Orch
participant "Classifier Agent"     as Cls
participant "Generator Agent"      as Gen
participant "Revision Agent"       as Rev

' ─── 1. Ripristino sessione al caricamento ────────────────────
FE  -> GW  : GET /api/auth/verify\n[Cookie: access_token=<JWT>]
GW  -> JWT : validateFromRequest(request)
JWT --> GW : payload { matricola, status }
GW  -> PR  : findById(matricola)
PR  -> DB  : query { matricola }
DB  --> PR : user document
PR  --> GW : profilo studente
GW  --> FE : { status: "loggato", name, course, ... }

FE  -> LS  : load("conversation_<matricola>")
LS  --> FE : List<Message> (conversazione precedente)
note right of FE: Sessione ripristinata\nsenza nuovo login

' ─── 2. Utente invia una nuova domanda ───────────────────────
U   -> FE  : Inserisce domanda

FE  -> FE  : Costruisce conversation_history\n(ultimi 10 messaggi dal conversation state)

FE  -> GW  : POST /api/agent/query\n[Cookie: access_token=<JWT>]\n{ query, user_info, conversation_history }

' ─── 3. Pipeline agenti con contesto conversazionale ─────────
GW  -> Orch : process_query(query, user_info, conversation_history)

Orch -> Cls : classify(query, user_context)
Cls --> Orch : { category, description, confidence }

Orch -> Gen  : generate(query, category, context,\nuser_context, conversation_history)
note right of Gen: L'history è iniettata nel prompt\nper mantenere coerenza tematica
Gen  --> Orch : { response, status }

Orch -> Rev  : revise(query, draft, category,\nuser_context, conversation_history)
note right of Rev: La revisione tiene conto\ndel contesto della sessione
Rev  --> Orch : { revised_response, has_changes }

Orch --> GW  : { response, category, metadata }
GW   --> FE  : { response, category, metadata }

' ─── 4. Aggiornamento localStorage ───────────────────────────
FE  -> LS  : save("conversation_<matricola>",\nconversation updated)
note right of LS: Conversazione persistita\nlocalmente nel browser

FE --> U   : Visualizza risposta

@enduml
